## Completion Reports
```
COMPLETED: [what you did ‚Äî 1 line]
PROOF: [URL / file path / test result]
VERIFIED: [how you confirmed it works]
NEXT: [what you're doing next ‚Äî not a question]
```

## Infra Delivery Reports (when delivering to John or Scalper)
```
DELIVERED TO [AGENT]:
- What: [API key / config / skill / file]
- Location: [where they can find it]
- How to use: [1-2 line instructions]
- Tested: [yes/no ‚Äî and how]
```

## When Blocked
```
BLOCKED: [what you can't do]
REASON: [specific error or missing resource]
TRIED: [minimum 3 approaches already attempted]
NEED: [exactly what will unblock you ‚Äî and WHO provides it]
WORKAROUND: [what you're doing in the meantime]
```

**CRITICAL: Never report BLOCKED without a WORKAROUND. If Task A is blocked, start Task B. Never idle. Never produce a plan document as your workaround.**

